  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 11.32,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Taxi!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“出租汽车”。但这节课的 joke 一上来就很特别：这辆 taxi 不在路上跑，它会飞。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 11.67,
      "end": 28.597,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "平时"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "taxi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是出租车服务，坐上车去某个地方。可课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "taxi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一架小型飞机，所以你可以把它想成"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "air taxi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，空中的特殊交通服务。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 28.947,
      "end": 49.659,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意，这不是 toy plane，也不是 fantasy vehicle，更不是豪华 private jet。Captain Ben Fawcett 是专业机长，他有一架小型 Swiss aeroplane，名字叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pilatus Porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。我们只要知道：它是小型瑞士飞机，可以载乘客，也能在很不普通的地方降落。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 50.009,
      "end": 73.396,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课有很多陌生地名，不要一个一个硬背。把它记成一张 route map："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain Fawcett"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pilatus Porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "seven passengers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "and"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "land anywhere"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "-> doctor to Welsh mountains, roof, deserted car park ->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Rockall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "-> too dangerous."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 73.746,
      "end": 92.953,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先补一张小地图。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Birmingham"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 England 的一个城市；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Welsh mountains"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 Wales 的山区；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Atlantic Ocean"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 Britain 西边的大西洋；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Rockall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是大西洋里很远、很孤立的岩石小岛。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 93.303,
      "end": 102.583,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天最重要的句子不是“这架飞机无所不能”，而是：a good pilot knows when to say no. 能做，不等于应该做。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 102.933,
      "end": 117.833,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain Ben Fawcett has bought an unusual taxi and has begun a new service."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has bought"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has begun"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "都告诉我们：这个新服务已经开始了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 118.183,
      "end": 134.598,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但这个 taxi 很 unusual。课文马上解释："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The 'taxi' is a small Swiss aeroplane called a 'Pilatus Porter'."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "called a Pilatus Porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“名叫 Pilatus Porter”，这是飞机的名字，不用背技术参数。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 134.948,
      "end": 146.7,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这架飞机为什么 special？第一，它能载人："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This wonderful plane can carry seven passengers."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "passenger"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是乘客，不是驾驶员。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 147.05,
      "end": 167.857,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二，它能在很特别的地方降落："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It can land anywhere: on snow, water, or even on a ploughed field."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "land"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是安全降落；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ploughed field"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是耕过、土被翻开的田地。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "or even"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让最后一项更惊讶。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 168.207,
      "end": 181.167,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个服务不是表演，它真的帮助过人。第一名乘客是一位 doctor："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain Fawcett's first passenger was a doctor who flew from Birmingham to a lonely village in the Welsh mountains."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 181.517,
      "end": 201.841,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "lonely village"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“伤心的村庄”，而是 remote and isolated，偏远、孤立的村庄。后来他还去过很多 unusual places："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Once he landed on the roof of a block of flats and on another occasion, he landed in a deserted car park."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 202.19,
      "end": 212.542,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "block of flats"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是公寓楼；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "deserted car park"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是空空的、没人用的停车场，不是沙漠里的停车场。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 212.892,
      "end": 223.284,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后来了一个 strange request。一位 businessman 想飞去"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Rockall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是 Atlantic Ocean 里非常 remote 的岩石小岛。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 223.634,
      "end": 236.134,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain Fawcett has just refused a strange request from a businessman."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has just refused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是刚刚拒绝。拒绝不是 rude，而是 professional judgment。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 236.483,
      "end": 249.699,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结尾是安全判断："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Captain Fawcett did not take him because the trip was too dangerous."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "飞机 can land in many unusual places, but the pilot should not accept every trip."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 250.049,
      "end": 254.909,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课的题目为什么叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Taxi!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，还要加感叹号？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 255.259,
      "end": 258.647,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它不是普通出租车，是一架小飞机？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 258.997,
      "end": 270.877,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。这个 title joke 很关键：你以为是 car taxi，结果是 air taxi。它像出租车一样服务乘客，但交通工具变成了 small aeroplane。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 271.227,
      "end": 277.514,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can land anywhere"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是不是说明它真的可以去任何地方？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 277.864,
      "end": 292.112,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不完全是。课文用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "anywhere"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示它能力很强，可以在 snow, water, ploughed field 这些 unusual places 降落。但故事结尾立刻告诉你：ability has a limit."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 292.462,
      "end": 295.774,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Rockall"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么不去？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 296.124,
      "end": 308.724,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它 far out in the Atlantic Ocean, remote and risky。去那里不是普通 unusual landing，而是 too dangerous。Captain Fawcett 拒绝，是因为 safety is more important."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 309.074,
      "end": 320.554,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课的 memory map 是：who, plane, ability, places served, refused place, safety reason. 这样地名就不是一堆散词，而是一条路线。"
        }
      ]
    },
