      "i": 41,
      "start": 433.167,
      "end": 436.158,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dangerous"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dangerous"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 436.508,
      "end": 438.284,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dangerous"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dangerous"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 438.634,
      "end": 448.066,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dangerous"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dangerous"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是危险的，不安全的。A road can be dangerous, a storm can be dangerous, and a trip can be dangerous."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 448.416,
      "end": 460.456,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "dangerous"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文最后说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the trip was too dangerous"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这不是说 Captain Fawcett 胆小，而是说 professional people must judge risk. Safety comes first."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 460.806,
      "end": 464.806,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 有三块，全部服务于这张 route map。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 465.156,
      "end": 480.595,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一块是 present perfect，表示这个服务从过去开始，到现在已经有了 history："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has bought"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has begun"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Since then, he has flown passengers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has just refused"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 480.945,
      "end": 493.529,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Since then"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "特别重要，意思是 from that time until now。从第一位 doctor 乘客以后，到现在为止，他已经飞去过很多 unusual places。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 493.879,
      "end": 509.158,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二块是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，表示能力："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can carry seven passengers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can land anywhere"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。注意"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面直接接动词原形 carry, land。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 509.508,
      "end": 524.396,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三块是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "because"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，给出安全理由："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He did not take him because the trip was too dangerous."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话把整课的价值观说清楚：can do is ability; should do is judgment."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 524.746,
      "end": 536.946,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的故事放到现代生活场景里。你经营一个 special transport service，你的交通工具可以去很多 unusual places，也可以载 several passengers。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 537.296,
      "end": 547.656,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但是今天有位 customer 提出一个 risky request：天气不好，他还想去一个 unsafe place。你要礼貌拒绝，同时说明原因。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 548.006,
      "end": 562.901,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以这样说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Our service can go to many unusual places. It can carry several passengers. But I cannot take you there today. The trip is too dangerous, and safety is more important."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 563.251,
      "end": 575.779,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "重点不是说 no 很凶，而是把 no 说得 responsible：先说明能力，再说明边界，最后用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "because"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "或 safety reason 解释。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 576.129,
      "end": 604.772,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课就到这。下面先做 ⓪ 跟读：听课文全文 -> 听原音 -> 录一句 -> 获取反馈，把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "unusual taxi"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "small Swiss aeroplane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Pilatus Porter"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "seven passengers"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "land anywhere"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "lonely village in the Welsh mountains"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "deserted car park"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "too dangerous"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "读顺。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 605.122,
      "end": 626.722,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "跟读完以后，再做 ① 生活场景，练习 special service 和 safe refusal；后面 ② 完形 ③ 中译英 ④ 英译中 ⑤ 默写 一条线做下来。做完以后，爸爸的邮箱里就会收到你今天的成绩。记住今天的核心：a good pilot knows when to say no."
        }
      ]
    }
